---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---

<div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300" id="use-cases">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-20 space-y-4 px-6 md:px-0">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
        Our Solutions
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 px-6 md:px-0">

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
          <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">🏡 Rental Certifier</h6>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Tamper-Proof Rental Applications</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6">
          Tisura enables rental platforms to verify that submitted documents (like pay slips or tax notices) truly originate from the trusted data sources and haven’t been altered. This prevents fraud and accelerates trust in the application process.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
          <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">💰 Loan Certifier</h6>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Trusted Docs for Smarter Lending</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6">
          Lenders use Tisura to ensure that key financial documents — bank statements, tax records, ID proofs — are authentic and sourced in real time. This reduces risk and boosts confidence in digital loan applications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
          <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">👨‍💻 GitHub Proofs</h6>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Prove What You’ve Built on GitHub</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6">
          Tisura allows developers to cryptographically prove authorship of their contributions on GitHub — commits, issues, or pull requests — ensuring verified ownership for hiring, grants, or funding applications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
          <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">🆔 Tisura Identity</h6>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Verifiable Identity Proofs, Without The Data Leak</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6">
          Tisura offers privacy-preserving identity verification: users prove their identity using cryptographic proofs without sharing personal details. Ideal for onboarding, age verification, or KYC without compromising privacy.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
